title: [Moving on Up]
description: Colorful planks of wood create fencelike walls across the room, the posts hung with twine-tied origami folded into the shapes of several equines, tortoises, and roltons.  Layered green wool rugs cover the planked floor, the runners leading towards several tin buckets filled with assorted treats.  Hung above the crossbeams are blown glass lanterns forged into fluffy clouds, the pieces lit by tiny teardrop-shaped votives casting a faint light across the shop.
